@DATABASE "Riptoff"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - R - Riptoff"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - R
                   ====================================

                                  Riptoff
                                  =======



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35427,183)"}          35427,183
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35528,255)"}          35528,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Rastan
@endnode
